name: Nothing Happened: The Complete Saga
description:
Part of the Girls' Greatest Joy Anthology.

A compilation of visual novels originally made for the 2015-2017 Global Game Jam and Ludum Dare 37.

Story

A young genius and his female AR companion are given missions at two Philippine universities, fulfilling their obligations to their boss. And at the same time, they must discover their own pasts that pave the way to what they are today.
